➜精致下午茶这样做，朋友和闺蜜都满意极了！
http://www.sohu.com/a/417462917_100001467	8877
<p class="ql-align-center">「下午茶」</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅是放松惬意的生活姿态，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更是一种优雅的社交方式。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天教大家在家做精致下午茶，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">优雅精致惬意的享受午后美好时光~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200910/b64b812ad0084f1786b450bd2546af69.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">首先我们🍰蛋挞料解冻后把蛋挞液倒入蛋挞皮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">亲身经验告诉大家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">倒入9分满即可~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">喜欢水果蛋挞的亲们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还可以在蛋挞上加点水果哦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">水果可以在这一步就放进去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">或是等蛋挞烤好出炉后再放在表面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200910/e959f86770804beaa0beb20f3f9dec33.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">🍓放入220°-240°烤箱烘烤15分钟即可出炉啦！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为每家的烤箱功率不同</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以时间和温度不是绝对的哈~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">烘烤前先预热10分钟，来确保烘烤的温度足够</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">后期要多看看上色情况，如果蛋挞皮已经很上色了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以调低或是关掉上管的温度哦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">😍色泽金黄，外酥里弹，好吃到飞起~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">🍦内馅奶香浓郁、软嫩香滑，回味无穷！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200910/5f803cc274a1440abc97558aada32309.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸡米花&amp;黑椒鸡块，拿出解冻后放入空气炸锅15分钟搞定！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">👉分享个小tips，可以在差不多9分钟的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">给鸡块和鸡米花翻个面哦，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样上色会均匀好看~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200910/e70243443ff94710a130ac349e102890.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">出锅后放在烘焙纸上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以买些印有图案的烘焙纸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">增加食物的质感~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">搭配个小碟子，挤点番茄酱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200910/693bb5e1871b442d8eb836875eadfafa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸡米花外脆里嫩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸡块黑椒味道浓郁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">搭配上酸甜可口的番茄酱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">🌽方便、美味、所有人都爱吃~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200910/456efe7e35a846229eb9ce5d57eba604.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想要下午茶有氛围</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以切一盘自己喜欢的水果哦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">切好的水果可以分一部分出来煮个水果茶</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">水果的小tips就是色彩多一点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这次我选择了黄黄的芒果、粉嘟嘟的水蜜桃、翠绿的青提</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">清新的柠檬，还有椭圆的猕猴桃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">水果茶里面多加了青桔和百香果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让紧绷的情绪溶化在这一份甜蜜中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200910/aebf9b18c2994b968ea6ea40fa8d3c6c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蛋挞、鸡块、鸡米花、水果茶</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都备好了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">选一本书，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">放一首动情的音乐，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">放空一下自已~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200910/9838fe3eb0534eb1a541a088094ad1b8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">约上三五好友，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">围坐一起，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">聊聊近况，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">品一份好心情！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一起享受慢下来的光阴！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是不是既有心意又有格调！</p>